| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-3354 — Recovery Inhibition (kairos)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 54cd5cac-15d8-5f97-9396-2e88cdbd6ce4"
